1)what is cloud?
a)a collection of data centres
  its a huge space which has all the services available
  
  2)what is cloud computing?
  a)cloud computing is a 
  
   * storing data/application on remote servers
   *processing data/application from serevers
   *accessing data/application via internet
   any where we can access data by cloud computing
   
   service models:SaaS  : software as a service :-
                         cloud provider leases applications or softwares which are owned by them to its client
				
	          PaaS  : platform as a service
			 No control over the underlying architecture including OS,storage,servers,etc
						  
		  iaaS  : infrastructure as a service
                         provides virtualized computing resources over the internet
